---
---

<section id="realworld" class="content-section realworld-section">
  <div class="section-container">
    <h3 class="section-title-left">Real-World Deployment Comparison on the Go1 Quadruped</h3>

    <div class="comparison-row">
      <div class="video-block">
        <div class="video-label baseline-label">TrajWorld (Baseline)</div>
        <div class="video-crop">
          <video id="trajworld-video" autoplay controls muted playsinline>
            <source src="/demos/trajworld-realworld-go1-pip.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
            Your browser does not support the video tag.
          </video>
          <span class="speed-badge">2x</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="video-block">
        <div class="video-label ours-label"><span class="ours-highlight">WestWorld (Ours)</span></div>
        <div class="video-crop">
          <video id="realworld-video" autoplay controls muted playsinline>
            <source src="/demos/realworld-go1-pip.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
            Your browser does not support the video tag.
          </video>
          <span class="speed-badge">2x</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-description" style="max-width:1400px; width:100%; margin: 1.5rem auto 0 auto;">
      <b>Our WestWorld outperforms the strongest baseline TrajWorld in real-world deployment on the Go1 quadruped.</b> Our method successfully completes the straight-walking task and reaches the goal, whereas TrajWorld fails to reliably stand up and move toward the target. Because MPPI relies on accurate long-horizon rollouts, TrajWorld's inaccurate predictions lead to poor action selection and control failure. In contrast, our method remains accurate enough to support stable real-world control, despite being trained only on an offline simulation dataset.
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style is:global>
  .realworld-section .section-container {
    max-width: 1400px;
  }
</style>

<style>
  .section-title-left {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #2a2f6c;
    margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .comparison-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .video-block {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .video-label {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
  }

  .baseline-label {
    background: #6b7280;
    color: white;
  }

  .ours-label {
    background: #2a2f6c;
    color: white;
  }

  .ours-highlight {
    background: #facc15;
    color: #1a1a2e;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .video-crop {
    width: 100%;
    background: #1a1a2e;
    position: relative;
  }

  .video-crop video {
    width: 100%;
    display: block;
  }

  .speed-badge {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 16px;
    left: 16px;
    color: white;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .section-description {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #333;
    text-align: left;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .comparison-row {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
